data.title: Boardwalk Resident Member Perks and Discount
data.meta_description: Alberta and Saskatchewan Resident Members receive free delivery when they order $25 or more from Pizza 73 in Western Canada.
data.text:
Since 1985, Pizza 73 continues to deliver on its promise to serve up a “Better meal. Better deal.” every time. With 25 varieties of speciality pizzas, over 20 different toppings, five styles of crust (Traditional Pan, Super Pan, Thin Crust, Sesame Seed and Gluten-Free), and seven types of sauce (Traditional, BBQ, Donair, Sriracha Honey Garlic, Pesto, Buffalo and Creamy Garlic), Pizza 73 has something for everyone.

Alberta and Saskatchewan Residents receive free delivery when they order $25 or more from Pizza 73.
